With a formula enriched with floral lip care ingredients,** the Dior Contour lip liner pencil perfectly combines bold color, 8h* of no-transfer wear and optimal comfort. The lips are flawlessly defined, their natural shape enhanced in one swipe.

Resistant to life's ups and downs, Dior Contour prolongs lipstick wear by 2h*** and limits feathering and settling into lip lines. The color is flawless and even all day long.

A limited-edition, travel-sized set featuring four all-new, summer-inspired nude shades of Matte Lipstick.
 
 Shades include:
 - Coconut
 - Guava
 - Lychee
 - Orange Blossom

This lip oil teams an intense lip care formula with a natural, flattering color finish for an ultra-luminous result. Dior Addict Lip Glow Oil adapts to all lip colors to bring out their rosy glow. Its non-greasy, non-sticky oil texture pushes the boundaries of shine and creates a smoothing film that shapes the lips with an almost magnifying mirror-shine effect.

Multi-use, Dior Addict Lip Glow Oil can be worn equally well on its own, as a primer under lipstick, or as a top coat for volumizing shine.
A full pigment liquid lip color formula that dries down to a weightless matte finish for smudge proof wearability and long lasting color.
